   keywords = {Carangidae,Gulf of Mexico,MOC,Mississippi River,generalized additive models,large midwater trawl},
   note = {nice intro stuff on importance of jack family<br/><br/>fish were collected in 4 surveys using nets and ID'ed to species level, estimates of abundance calculated<br/><br/>good description of GAM methods},
